```
{{/markdown}}

  <h3>Dismiss buttons</h3>
  <p>Mobile Safari browser (and Mobile Opera), in addition to the <code>data-dismiss="alert"</code> attribute, require an <code>href="#"</code> for the dismissal of alerts when using an <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> tag.</p>

{{#markdown}}
```markup
<a href="#" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</a>
```
{{/markdown}}

  <p>Alternatively, you may use a <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> element with the data attribute, which we have opted to do. When using <code>&lt;button&gt;</code>, you must include <code>type="button"</code> or your forms may not submit.</p>

{{#markdown}}
```markup
<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
```
{{/markdown}}

